        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-8">
        <%= image_tag  "duncan.jpg", class: "featurette-image img-circle img-responsive pull-left", alt: "Adult PBGV with tie." %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <h2 class="text-center"><%= link_to "Click here to see our litters!", "#"%></h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="divider">
  Duncan is the best dog ever!!!
</div>
